claim.claim-text:
Opening mechanism comprising:
- a locking element (38) movably arranged along a locking element axis;
- a blocking element (12) movably arranged along a blocking element axis, attacking in a locking position with a first end (16) at the locking element (38), whereby the locking element (38) is blocked in its freedom of movement, and which is hook-shaped at its second end (14);
- a spring element (32) acting along the locking element axis, and
- an actuating element (26) which is so configured that it can transfer the blocking element (12) by attacking at the hook-shaped second end (14) from a closed position into an open position, whereby the blocking element (12) releases the locking element (38).
